â”œâ”€ Transporter info
â”œâ”€ Vehicle details
â”œâ”€ Pickup location (GPS coordinates)
â”œâ”€ Seal verification
â”œâ”€ Status: IN_TRANSIT
â””â”€ Ownership: Still with Distributor (critical!)
    â†“
