â”œâ”€ Real-time vehicle location visible on dashboard
â”œâ”€ Route map shows
â””â”€ Estimated time remaining
```

### Step 6: Transporter Logs Temperature (Continuous)

```
Every 4 hours during transport:
    â†“
Driver (or automated IoT sensor) logs:
â”œâ”€ Current temperature
â”œâ”€ Current location (GPS)
â”œâ”€ Vehicle status
â”œâ”€ Package seal status
â””â”€ Any issues encountered
    â†“
Smart contract creates Block #6, #7, #8... (Multiple)
â”œâ”€ TemperatureLoggedByTransporter
â”œâ”€ Timestamp
â”œâ”€ Location
â”œâ”€ Temperature reading
â””â”€ Status remains: IN_TRANSIT
    â†“
Monitoring system:
â”œâ”€ Real-time alerts if temperature breaches
â”œâ”€ SMS sent to stakeholders if temp out of range
â”œâ”€ Dashboard shows live temperature graph
â””â”€ Historical data stored immutably
```

### Step 7: Transporter Completes Delivery

```
