LOGIN FLOW:

User clicks "Connect Wallet"
    â†“
MetaMask opens
    â†“
User approves connection
    â†“
Frontend gets Ethereum address
    â†“
Backend queries Users collection:
    WHERE ethereumAddress = "0x742d35Cc6634C0532925a3b844Bc91e7d8e7f2D5"
    â†“
Backend finds user record:
    {role: "MANUFACTURER", permissions: [...]}
    â†“
Backend creates JWT token with role encoded
    â†“
Frontend stores token in localStorage
    â†“
User logged in to their dashboard
    â†“
All API calls include JWT token
    â†“
Backend middleware verifies token and permissions
    before allowing action
```

