# COMPLETE SYSTEM DESIGN SUMMARY

## Unified Blockchain Network

âœ… **SINGLE blockchain shared by all companies**
âœ… **Role-based access control (RBAC)**
âœ… **Company-specific dashboards**
âœ… **NO separate chains per company**
âœ… **Immutable audit trail**
âœ… **Real-time tracking**
âœ… **Public verification (no login)**

## Tech Stack

âœ… **Blockchain:** Ethereum Sepolia Testnet â†’ Hyperledger Besu (later)
âœ… **Smart Contracts:** Solidity + Hardhat
âœ… **Backend:** Node.js + Express.js
âœ… **Database:** MongoDB
âœ… **Frontend:** React.js
âœ… **Wallet:** MetaMask
âœ… **Cost:** 100% FREE

## Key Features

âœ… **Manufacturer:** Create batches, serialize, assign to distributors
âœ… **Distributor:** Accept batches, create shipments, assign transporters
âœ… **Transporter:** Pick up, track temperature, deliver packages
âœ… **Pharmacy:** Accept delivery, accept ownership, dispense to patients
âœ… **Public:** Verify authenticity via QR code (no login)
âœ… **Admin:** Monitor, verify, dispute resolution, compliance reporting

## Blockchain Transactions

Each action creates immutable block:
- Block #1: BatchCreated
- Block #2: BatchTransferred
- Block #3: DistributorAcceptedBatch
- Block #4: ShipmentCreatedByDistributor
- Block #5-7: TemperatureLoggedByTransporter (multiple)
- Block #8: TransportDeliveryCompletedByTransporter
- Block #9: PharmacyAcceptedDelivery (OWNERSHIP TRANSFER)
- Block #10: DispensingEventToPatient

Complete supply chain â†’ Immutable proof of authenticity
